about.summary: A jazzy skin for the Django Admin-Interface

name: django-grappelli
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "django-grappelli" %}
{% set version = "3.0.8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/django-grappelli-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0c24a0128a8e94b0f251a99d71b96738e4cf546d20fd993d03b26c05c8642fdd

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - django

test:
  imports:
    - grappelli
    - grappelli.templatetags
    - grappelli.views
    - grappelli.dashboard
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://django-grappelli.readthedocs.org
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A jazzy skin for the Django Admin-Interface

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kwilcox
    - ocefpaf
